tteint</span> <span class="hps">en 90 minutes.</span></span></li><li><span class="hps">Ne prenez pas</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Malegra FXT</span> <span class="hps">plus souvent</span> <span class="hps">qu'une fois par jour</span><span>.</span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Si vous</span> <span class="hps">manquez une dose de</span> <span class="hps">Malegra FXT</span> <span class="hps">et vous avez toujours</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'intention d'avoir</span><span class="hps alt-edited"> l'activit&eacute; sexuelle</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">prenez-la d&egrave;s</span> <span class="hps">que vous vous souvenez</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Continuez &agrave; la</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">prendre tel qu'indiqu&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">par votre m&eacute;decin.</span></span></li></ul><p><strong><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">DOSAGE</span></span></strong></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Prenez le</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">m&eacute;decine comme est indiqu&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">par votre m&eacute;decin.</span></span></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Si vous</span> <span class="hps">manquez une dose de</span> <span class="hps">Malegra</span> F<span class="hps">XT</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">utilisez-la d&egrave;s</span> <span class="hps">que possible</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Si</span> <span class="hps">c'est presque le temps</span> <span class="hps">pour votre</span> <span class="hps">dose suivante, sautez</span> <span class="hps">la dose oubli&eacute;e et</span> <span class="hps">reprenez votre</span> <span class="hps">programme de dosage r&eacute;gulier</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">N'utilisez pas 2</span> <span class="hps">doses &agrave; la fois</span><span>.</span></span></p><p><strong><span lang="fr">CONSERVATION</span></strong></p><p><span lang="fr"><spa