ythromycine</span><span>)</span><span>,</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">les analg&eacute;siques</span> <span class="hps">narcotiques (par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, dihydrocod&eacute;ine</span><span>)</span><span>,</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>ou</span> <span class="hps">t&eacute;lithromycine</span><span>, car ils peuvent</span> <span class="hps">augmenter le</span> <span class="hps">risque d'effets secondaires</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">de </span></span><br />Malegra FXT</li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Bosentan ou rifampin</span><span>, car il</span> <span class="hps">peut diminuer l'efficacit&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">de </span></span>Malegra FXT.</li></ul><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Ce n'est pas</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">une liste compl&egrave;te</span> <span class="hps">de toutes les interactions</span> <span class="hps">qui peuvent se produire</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Demandez &agrave; votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin si </span></span>Malegra FXT <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">peut interagir</span> <span class="hps">avec d'autres </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">m&eacute;dicaments</span> <span class="hps">que vous prenez.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Consultez votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin avant de commencer</span><span>, abandonner ou</span> <span class="hps">modifier la dose de</span> <span class="hps">tout m&eacute;dicament.</span></span></p><p><strong>Information de s&eacute;curit&eacute; importante:</strong></p><ul><li>Malegra FXT <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">peut causer le vertige</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">la somnolence</span><span>, l'&eacute;vanouissement,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou une vision floue</span><span>. </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Ces</span> <span class="hps">effets</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peuvent &ecirc;tre pires si</span> <span class="hps">vous la prenez</span> <span class="hps">avec de l'alcool</span> <span class="hps">ou certains m&eacute;dicaments. </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Utilisez </span></span>Malegra FXT <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">avec prudence</span><span>. </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Ne </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">conduisez pas</span> <span class="hps">une auto ou n'accomplissez pas</span> <span class="hps">d'autres</span> <span class="hps">t&acirc;ches</span> <span class="hps">dangereux jusqu'&agrave; ce que</span> <span class="hps">vous savez comment</span> <span class="hps">vous y r&eacute;agissez</span><span>.</span></span></li><li>Malegra FXT <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">peut causer le vertige</span> <span class="hps">ou l'&eacute;vanouissement; </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">l'alcool</span><span>, le temps chaud</span><span>, l'exercice</span><span class="alt-edited">, la fi&egrave;vre</span> <span class="hps">peuvent augmenter ces effets</span><span>. </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Pour les pr&eacute;venir,</span> <span class="hps">essayez de vous asseoir</span> <span class="hps">ou rester debout </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">lentement</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">surtout le </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">matin</span><span>. </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Asseyez-vous</span> <span class="hps">ou allongez-vous</span> <span class="hps">au premier signe</